    Stopping criteria for self training

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      Airbag
      (Leistner et al., 2009), based on Out of Bag Error estimate of Random Forest (applicable only if the base method for the Self Training is Random Forest)
      Iterations
      Iterations - stop after specified number of iterations
      NoneAdded
      If no instance met the UnlabeledCriteria, i.e., no instance was added to the training set
